&lt;p&gt;~ 385524004  │ Lower limit of reference range (qualifier value) │  No specific guidance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Where required codes are unavailable consideration should be given to the submission of a new code request to UK SNOMED CT request submission portal (see https://isd.digital.nhs.uk/rsp/user/guest/home.jsf). Contact info@thePRSB.org for further information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

