&lt;p&gt;Diabetes Distress Scale (DDS) 2 item ** │ 909401000000106 │ Diabetes Distress Scale 2 item (assessment scale) │ No specific guidance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DDS 17 item ** │ 909441000000109 │ Diabetes Distress Scale 17 item (assessment scale) │ Validated for use by people with type 2 diabetes (see https://diabetesdistress.org/dd-assess-score-3).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;T1-DDS ** │ 1373521000000101  │ Type 1 Diabetes Distress Scale (assessment scale) │ Validated for use by people with type 1 diabetes. For rationale (see https://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2Fj.jdiacomp.2015.01.012).&lt;/p&gt;
