&lt;p&gt;Waterlow pressure sore risk score │ 278897004 │ Waterlow pressure sore risk score (assessment scale) │ No specific guidance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mobility and activities of daily living&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Barthel ADL index │ 273302005 │ Barthel index (assessment scale) │ Descendent or self of concept (including original, UK or modified scales).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Instrumental activities of daily living (I-ADL) │ 273534002 │ Instrumental activities of daily living (assessment scale) │ No specific guidance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pain assessment&lt;/p&gt;
