                                &lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;For a review of features specific to advanced diabetes devices such as low glucose suspend, predictive low glucose suspend (PLGS) and hybrid closed loop (HCL) (see https://dx.doi.org/10.1089%2Fdia.2019.0105).&lt;br clear="none"/&gt;
