                                    &lt;/strong&gt;
                                &lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;~New code request │ Percentage of successful data capture time to total expected insulin pump wear time using insulin pump device (observable entity) │ Equal of concept.&lt;/div&gt;
